parameters: Chronos Thief Member: Damn, things have gone bad.

Thug: What are you going to do!? If the opponent is Armada,
I won't cooperate, you know!

Thug: If we make an enemy out of that person, we won't have
a place to hide in Valeria anymore--

Chronos Thief Member: Shut up! We have to report to the boss
that our squad has been taken down.
Thug: Who the hell are you?!

Clea: This is a request from Armada. I will hand you over to
the guards.

Chronos Thief Member: No need to panic... If Armada isn't
here, we still have a good chance to win.

Chronos Thief Member: And besides, she's quite a beauty.
It'll be a nice souvenir--

Thief Nora: W-What is it? I can fight too, so don't
underestimate me!

Chronos Thief Member: The crimson scarf... Hey, don't you
dare kill the big woman.

Chronos Thief Member: Don't underestimate the Chronos Thief
Guild, here we go!!
Clea: I'll go over there too.

Chronos Thief Member: You're giving us trouble... Get rid of
the big one.

Chronos Thief Member: If you're wearing a crimson scarf,
then you must be a member of the Ema Thief Guild.

Chronos Thief Member: I don't want to pick a fight with such
a crazy group.

Chronos Thief Member: Well, now it's just you left. I'll
make you pay for causing such a commotion.
Would you like to skip the adult scene?

Do you want to retry the battle? If you choose No, it will
result in a game over.
Clea: Then I'll leave it to the guards.

Chronos Thief Member: Armada... and the Emma Thief Guild...
there's no luck with them.
Thief Nora: Do you know about the Emma Thief Guild!?

Chronos Thief Member: Ah, they're famous for being clueless
idiots.

Chronos Thief Member: You guys are a bunch of rabid dogs who
bite indiscriminately, unable to live long... ugh...

Thief Nora: ...That's why we need it. A proof that we don't
have to cause any more trouble, the Dragon's Eye.

Clea: Let's call back the guards and also report to Armada-
san.
